comments: Looney (GSW) does not establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Westbrook (WAS) and extends his lower body into Westbrook's back which affect his ability to defend around the pick.
Beal (WAS) legally contests Curry's (GSW) jump shot attempt.
Curry (GSW) slightly extends his leg into the lower body of Beal (WAS) during his jump shot attempt. The contact however does not affect Beal's (WAS) ability to contest the shot.
Neto (WAS) makes contact with Oubre Jr.'s (GSW) arm that affects his shot near the rim.
Looney (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Westbrook (WAS) firms up and absorbs the contact.
Wiggins (GSW) makes marginal contact to the arm of Beal (WAS) after the release that does not affect his finish at the rim.
Bonga (WAS) makes marginal contact to the body of Curry (GSW) during the drive that he is able to move through and his SQBR is not affected.
Poole (GSW) maintains a legal guarding position on Beal (WAS) during the drive as he beats him to the spot. The contact that occurs is marginal and does not affect Beal's (WAS) SQBR.
Beal (WAS) makes marginal contact to the body of Curry (GSW) during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Poole (GSW) commits a take foul on Bertans (WAS).
